TITLE: Cloneable PyO3 Class Implementation
DESCRIPTION: Shows how to implement a cloneable PyO3 class using #[derive(Clone)] and how to handle class instances passed by value.
SOURCE: https://github.com/PyO3/pyo3/blob/main/guide/src/class.md#2025-04-16_snippet_23

LANGUAGE: rust
CODE:
```
#[pyclass]
#[derive(Clone)]
struct MyClass {
    my_field: Box<i32>,
}

#[pyfunction]
fn dissamble_clone(my_class: MyClass) {
    let MyClass { mut my_field } = my_class;
    *my_field += 1;
}
```

