TITLE: Runtime Python Version Check Example
DESCRIPTION: Demonstrates how to check Python version at runtime using PyO3's version_info API
SOURCE: https://github.com/PyO3/pyo3/blob/main/guide/src/building-and-distribution/multiple-python-versions.md#2025-04-16_snippet_3

LANGUAGE: rust
CODE:
```
use pyo3::Python;

Python::with_gil(|py| {
    // PyO3 supports Python 3.7 and up.
    assert!(py.version_info() >= (3, 7));
    assert!(py.version_info() >= (3, 7, 0));
});
```

